# vhs Layer 4 — Onboarding 5-step preflight (env unset, fresh state)
Output specs/integration-verification/frames/vhs-08-onboarding.gif
Output specs/integration-verification/frames/vhs-08-onboarding.txt
Set Shell "bash"
Set FontSize 14
Set FontFamily "JetBrains Mono"
Set Width 1600
Set Height 900
Set Theme "TokyoNightStorm"
Hide
Type "rm -rf ~/.kosmos/memdir/user/onboarding && cd /Users/um-yunsang/KOSMOS/tui && bun run tui"
Enter
Sleep 6s
Show
Screenshot specs/integration-verification/frames/vhs-08-keyframe-1-step1-preflight.png
Sleep 500ms
Ctrl+C
Sleep 500ms
Ctrl+C
Sleep 1s
